#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Kingsman Umbrella"
msgstr "王牌特工雨伞"

#. ~ Description for Kingsman Umbrella
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds the Umbrella gun from Kingsman - The Secret Service."
msgstr "添加来自《王牌特工：特工学院》的雨伞枪。"

#: .\apparel\armor.json
msgid "pair of boots"
msgid_plural "pairs of boots"
msgstr[0] "一双靴子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of boots', 'str_pl': 'pairs of boots'}
#: .\apparel\armor.json
msgid ""
"Boots that seem to have a spring loaded knife in their toe.  Could be used "
"as a weapon if taken off and held."
msgstr "这双靴子的脚尖似乎装有弹簧刀。脱下后手持可作武器使用。"

#: .\apparel\clothing.json
msgid "light overcoat"
msgid_plural "light overcoats"
msgstr[0] "轻薄大衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'light overcoat'}
#: .\apparel\clothing.json
msgid "A thin cotton overcoat, look stylish even during the catacylsm."
msgstr "一件薄棉大衣，即便在末世浩劫中也能保持时尚。"

#: .\apparel\clothing.json
msgid "suit jacket"
msgid_plural "suit jackets"
msgstr[0] "西装外套"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'suit jacket'}
#: .\apparel\clothing.json
msgid ""
"A jacket meant to go over a suit.  Who says you can't look nice during the "
"apocalypse?"
msgstr "一件套在西装外的外套。谁说末世中不能穿得体面？"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'light overcoat'}
#: .\apparel\clothing.json
msgid ""
"A thin cotton overcoat, look stylish when you brandish your .44 Magnum."
msgstr "一件薄棉大衣，在你挥舞.44马格南时显得格外潇洒。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'suit jacket'}
#: .\apparel\clothing.json
msgid ""
"A jacket meant to go over a suit.  Who says you can't be great looking "
"during a gunfight?"
msgstr "一件套在西装外的外套。谁说枪战中不能保持帅气？"

#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid "pair of square framed glasses"
msgid_plural "pairs of square framed glasses"
msgstr[0] "一副方框眼镜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of square framed glasses', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of square framed glasses'}
#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid ""
"A pair of square framed glasses, look sylish while the world is in ruin."
msgstr "一副方框眼镜，在世界废墟中仍显时尚。"

#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid "silver watch"
msgid_plural "silver watches"
msgstr[0] "银表"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'silver watch', 'str_pl': 'silver watches'}
#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid "A self-winding silver watch, look great while punching zombies."
msgstr "一块自动上链的银表，在痛击僵尸时显得格外有型。"

#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid "pair of round frame glasses"
msgid_plural "pairs of round frame glasses"
msgstr[0] "一副圆框眼镜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pair of round frame glasses', 'str_pl': 'pairs
#. of round frame glasses'}
#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid ""
"A pair of rounded frame glasses, look nice even while you're being grabbed "
"at my zombies."
msgstr "一副圆框眼镜，即便在被僵尸抓扯时也能保持体面。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'silver watch', 'str_pl': 'silver watches'}
#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid ""
"A self-winding silver watch, it's leather band feels oddly confortable "
"against your skin."
msgstr "一块自动上链的银表，其皮革表带贴肤异常舒适。"

#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid "cowboy hat"
msgid_plural "cowboy hats"
msgstr[0] "牛仔帽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cowboy hat'}
#: .\apparel\other.json
msgid ""
"Whether hunting bobcats, fixing up the ranch, or dueling to the death with "
"zombies, this your hat!"
msgstr "无论是猎杀山猫、打理牧场，还是与僵尸决一死战，这顶帽子都适合你！"

#: .\misc\materials.json
msgid "stainless steel"
msgstr "不锈钢"

#: .\misc\materials.json
msgid "dented"
msgstr "凹陷的"

#: .\misc\materials.json
msgid "scratched"
msgstr "刮伤"

#: .\misc\materials.json
msgid "marked"
msgstr "标记"

#: .\misc\materials.json
msgid "smashed"
msgstr "砸碎"

#: .\misc\materials.json
msgid "shattered"
msgstr "粉碎"

#: .\weapons\weapon.json
msgid "umbrella gun"
msgid_plural "umbrella guns"
msgstr[0] "雨伞枪"

#: .\weapons\weapon.json
msgid ""
"An umbrella that looks like it came straight out of a movie, it seems to be "
"bulletproof."
msgstr "一把看起来像是直接从电影里拿出来的雨伞，它似乎是防弹的。"

#. ~ Use action menu_text for {'str': 'umbrella gun'}.
#: .\weapons\weapon.json
msgid "Open Umbrella"
msgstr "打开雨伞"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'umbrella gun'}.
#: .\weapons\weapon.json
msgid "You open up the umbrella."
msgstr "你打开了雨伞。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'umbrella gun'}
#: .\weapons\weapon.json
msgid ""
"An umbrella that looks like it came straight out of a movie.  It is closed."
msgstr "一把看起来像是直接从电影里拿出来的雨伞。它是合上的。"

#: .\weapons\weapon.json
msgid ".44 Magnum"
msgid_plural ".44 Magnum"
msgstr[0] ".44 马格南"

#: .\weapons\weapon.json
msgid ""
"One of the most famous guns in the world, the .44 Magnum is known for being "
"great to dispatch an opponent in a gun duel."
msgstr "世界上最著名的枪支之一，.44 马格南以在枪战中高效解决对手而闻名。"
